  <summary date="2019-08-15T11:50:05Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Supporting Kinship Connections Act

This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to provide grants for developing, enhancing, or evaluating kinship navigator programs; such programs help grandparents and other relative caregivers find and use services to meet the needs of the caregivers and the children they are raising.</summary>
